caption:
IBS isn’t one-size-fits-all! 🌟 Did you know there are three types?
🚽 IBS-D (Diarrhea dominant) 
🚽 IBS-C (Constipation dominant) 
🚽 IBS-M (Mixed—both diarrhea and constipation, sometimes on the same day!) 

✨IBS-Smart may be something to consider if you’re experiencing frustrating diarrhea symptoms and can be done with the Trio-Smart breath test that may be helpful for those experiencing more bloating (especially after eating), constipation and/or diarrhea symptoms. Get the clarity you deserve! 

#KnowYourIBS #GutHealthSolutions #TrioSmart #IBSSmart
